1 heartjure ❤️ ⚡️
Welcome stranger,
The following book encompasses a small study over one of Kaggle’s Heart Attack datasets
It’s a domain that’s very well studied. I am not seeking to produce any groundbreaking findings here but just to make a few nice visualisations and perhaps fit a few good models for the purposes to showcase my data science and machine learning skills
